### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### 2. Get All Appointments (Initially Empty)
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments

###

### 3. Book a Valid Appointment
# @name createAppointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "businessType": "hair_salon",
  "service": "Haircut",
  "date": "2026-07-10",
  "time": "17:00"
}

###

### 4. Extract ID and Fetch the Created Appointment
# Note: Copy the id from the step 3 response and replace the ID below manually
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/8ad9bcc0-08d2-4ac0-b41e-acf0a19a5564

###

### 5. Test Validation Error (Invalid Business Type)
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane",
  "phone": "123",
  "businessType": "spa",
  "service": "Haircut",
  "date": "2026-07-10",
  "time": "17:00"
}

###

### 6. Cancel / Delete an Appointment
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/appointments/replace_with_actual_id_from_response